  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test two strategies to reduce the risk of contracting Human
      Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) or Hepatitis C Virus (HCV) by reducing risk behaviors in
      patients undergoing drug detoxification.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
